volley upon the Whigs, who have just succeeded in
dragging the wounded Gardinier out of the mele.
Severa fall, but their death is avenged on the
instant
;
yet dearly avenged, for the blow which
follows
,
while it terminates the battle, concludes the
existence of one of the most gallant spirits
